Package: CCNV
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Antonia", "Gocke", , "an.gocke@uke.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package can read idats and infers the copy number data. It 
    then segments the data, either cumulatively or consecutively and can then 
    create cumulative copy number variation plots and the corresponding 
    frequency plots.
